--// Functions 


MakeCategory(Name:string) - Returns a container and adds a category 
MakeSubCategory(Name, Container) - Returns a subcategory, the container should deprive from MakeCategory
Title(Name) - update the title of the main window
AddThread(Thread) - The Thread should be able to have :Disconnect called. :Disconnect will be called on this Thread when the UI closes

MakeRow(Name, {Type, Value, Container}) - Returns a row 
Value - an optional ValueBase instance such as a boolvalue or stringvalue ( for example, if the type is string, you'd want a stringvalue.)
Container - a container from the MakeCategory function 
Type - a string that can be one of - {"Bool", "Button", "String"} - caps don't matter
--




--// Other 

Converted - a table containing all of the UIs contents

--// Discreteis
 
